text.tspan: Encouragement — For Living in the Body
exercise our spirit with the saints
our Christ to one another we’re built up
That you would be filled fully,
with our enjoyment of the Lord,
And if we do our part
to spend time to receive Him in the Word,
So why not turn to Christ right now?
Simply eat Him that is how.
If we’re soaked and filled up to the brim,
We can’t help but express Him.
That you would be filled fully,
